							Steven R. Hagen, Ph.D.












Steven Hagen is responsible for quality and regulatory affairs as well as technical operations. Prior to this, he was responsible for API and drug product manufacturing operations globally, including chemical and pharmaceutical development activities.
Before joining AMRI, Dr. Hagen served as a director of analytical development for Pfizer, Inc., and was an analytical biochemist with Ribi ImmunoChem Research, Inc. He received a bachelor’s in biology from Lawrence University, as well as a master’s degree in botany and a Ph.D. in biochemistry, both from the University of Idaho.








